</ref> and the launching of the official website.<ref>{{cite news
  | last = Braxton
  | first = Arnold
  | title = Tecmo unveils the official Ninja Gaiden Website
  | publisher = PopCultureShock
  | date = [[2004-03-04]]
  | url = http://www.popcultureshock.com/news.php?id=587
  | accessdate = 2007-08-21 }}
</ref> Those who had pre-ordered the game on Tecmo's site can purchase ''Ninja Gaiden'' merchandises at a discount.<ref>{{cite news
  | author = z36
